data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom home, offering a perfect blend of modern living and natural beauty. As you step inside, you'll immediately appreciate the sense of space and openness that defines this residence. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting ample counter space, modern appliances, and a cozy breakfast nook that invites you to start your day with the warm glow of natural light. For those special occasions and family gatherings, a formal dining area is ready to create lasting memories around the dinner table. Working from home? No problem. This home provides a versatile office space, ensuring you have a dedicated area for productivity and focus. Outside, your private backyard oasis is enclosed by a privacy fence, offering a lush green retreat. What truly sets this property apart is the serene woods behind, providing not only privacy but also a beautiful natural view. Location-wise, you're in close proximity to the upcoming waterfront district, promising exciting developments and attractions that will enhance your lifestyle and property value! AND for your peace of mind a 1 year home warranty!!
